cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IT. 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision tasks, specifically measuring similarity between patches in images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel approach to patch matching using self-similarity behavior, which falls under the scope of machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories as well. Additionally, the paper tests the proposed method on three distinct problems, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
